source.name: 2010 Administrative Law Judge Initial Decisions
source.description: The initial decisions issued by administrative law judges in 2010 that contains findings of fact, legal conclusions, and an order that often contains a sanction. These initial decisions follow hearings on allegations of securities law violations initiated in most cases by the Commission's Division of Enforcement.
